{"word":"κοιμάω","slug":"κοιμάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰοιμάω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κεῖμαι\">κεῖμαι</a></el>] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp> sleep,</b> in its central <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mng.\">mng.</a> <b><a href='B:470 28:13'>Mt 28:13</a>; <a href='B:490 22:45'>Lk 22:45</a>; <a href='B:500 11:12'>J 11:12</a>; <a href='B:510 12:6'>Ac 12:6</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp> sleep,</b> of sleep in sense of die, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fig.\">fig.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> of 1, defined by context <b><a href='B:470 27:52'>Mt 27:52</a>; <a href='B:500 11:11'>J 11:11</a>; <a href='B:510 7:60'>Ac 7:60</a>; <a href='B:530 7:39'>1 Cor 7:39</a>; <a href='B:530 15:6'>15:6</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a>; <b><a href='B:590 4:13-15'>1 Th 4:13-15</a>; <a href='B:680 3:4'>2 Pt 3:4</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κοιλία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κοίμησις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}